{"tid":212502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英：曾考慮到被告人士年紀小　　想過運用特赦權力。","createTime":"2017-04-22T13:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-23T01:49:47.000Z","uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d82e2e781c61f7687a304889f0bb4149672a700b","tid":212502,"uid":58099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/m13376cyleung200x0e63.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fm13376cyleung200x0e63.png&h=17239add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉早前提出特赦佔中參與者、「七警」和退休警司朱經緯等，最後收回言論，特首梁振英指出，當有人提出特赦建議後，曾考慮到被告人士年紀小，想過運用特赦權力。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，若案件已進入司法程序，他不能特赦被告，強調特赦權力不能凌駕司法程序。梁振英又稱，檢察工作由律政司及刑事檢控專員負責，特首或行政部門都不能干預"},{"pid":"23358a71bbc5f61c4ec0303eb160e4b3550a0daa","tid":212502,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:13:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d29989b4f462350ca1df98b37c0370b86c353db3","tid":212502,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"但係又想開槍殺學生"},{"pid":"0a3844fbe33387c7636e31072d7032c69fb9d1f8","tid":212502,"uid":89608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:33:43.000Z","msg":"撚一撚, 又一堆港豬吹奏梁特既偉大 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e00537552b607d3e2fe1a30d36d3a53748326b","tid":212502,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:39:43.000Z","msg":"鱷魚淚....."},{"pid":"dff797bce5c3e5272ac7ab8e6c94555688da19ff","tid":212502,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:41:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"302daf6b0a614c7bf53d641972ed64dcaa802ed2","tid":212502,"uid":36981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實cy都唔係咁差姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />